channel.title: Problem
channel.description:
Yes. It's a webclient problem. Yes. It's the "Requesting Title Screen" problem.
Well, the main problem is....I cannot figure out why this is happening. Generally that would mean it cannot find the title screen...Correct...? So, why then....When I do not use the client in a browser it loads perfectly fine?
Does anyone know what the problem may be?
